Is anything wrong?

00:19:03.768 --> 00:19:06.396 position:50% align:center
- Sorry, I'm gonna go take
a bath.

00:19:07.814 --> 00:19:10.400 position:50% align:center
I don't understand at all.

00:19:10.692 --> 00:19:14.195 position:50% align:center
Am I doing it
in the wrong way somehow?

