from somewhere out there, right?

00:19:18.116 --> 00:19:21.036 position:50% align:center
Please, answer me, Asumi.

00:19:21.494 --> 00:19:22.537 position:50% align:center
- Shuta.
- Asumi.

00:19:22.620 --> 00:19:23.747 position:50% align:center
- When you get older,

00:19:23.830 --> 00:19:25.457 position:50% align:center
