- Oh, really?

00:19:27.834 --> 00:19:29.169 position:50% align:center
- Mm, yeah.

00:19:29.252 --> 00:19:31.338 position:50% align:center
I was telling my mom
all about you earlier.

00:19:31.421 --> 00:19:34.424 position:50% align:center
Delivering that bread
to everybody in place of Ran.

00:19:34.507 --> 00:19:37.635 position:50% align:center
You looked just like a hero.
- Oh, you mean the crusts.

00:19:37.719 --> 00:19:39.471 position:50% align:center
- The reason Takara Food Bank

00:19:39.554 --> 00:19:41.222 position:50% align:center
