Shu.

00:19:41.306 --> 00:19:42.807 position:50% align:center
- [gasps]

00:19:42.891 --> 00:19:44.351 position:50% align:center
I've made up my mind!

00:19:44.434 --> 00:19:46.478 position:50% align:center
In the future
I'll become a hero!

00:19:46.561 --> 00:19:48.438 position:50% align:center
I'll make everybody smile!

