Oh, but I'm gonna have to run
the bakery as well.

00:19:51.274 --> 00:19:53.485 position:50% align:center
Ah, geez!
I can't choose!

00:19:53.568 --> 00:19:55.153 position:50% align:center
Ah!
- Why not do both?

00:19:55.236 --> 00:19:56.988 position:50% align:center
- Huh?
- You'll bake bread

00:19:57.072 --> 00:19:59.657 position:50% align:center
and be a hero.
