00:19:59.741 --> 00:20:01.242 position:50% align:center
you know?

00:20:01.743 --> 00:20:03.745 position:50% align:center
[vacuum sucking]
- [humming]

00:20:04.287 --> 00:20:05.246 position:50% align:center
Oh?

00:20:06.122 --> 00:20:07.665 position:50% align:center
'Scuse me, Shuta?

00:20:08.917 --> 00:20:10.835 position:50% align:center
Huh?
He's gone?

00:20:10.919 --> 00:20:12.545 position:50% align:center
Oh, no, wait!
This can't be!

00:20:13.088 --> 00:20:14.714 position:50% align:center
No, no, no, no, no, no, no!

00:20:14.798 --> 00:20:16.174 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:20:18.968 --> 00:20:21.304 position:50% align:center
Hey, Shuta!
Please wake up!

00:20:22.180 --> 00:20:23.306 position:50% align:center
Uh-oh.

00:20:23.682 --> 00:20:24.808 position:50% align:center
He's not breathing!

00:20:25.058 --> 00:20:27.435 position:50% align:center
[whimpers]

00:20:27.519 --> 00:20:29.187 position:50% align:center
Oh, I'm so sorry, Ran!

00:20:29.270 --> 00:20:30.939 position:50% align:center
I'm sorry, Mari!

00:20:31.940 --> 00:20:35.068 position:50% align:center
[whimpering]

00:20:37.195 --> 00:20:38.697 position:50% align:center
It's you!

00:20:39.155 --> 00:20:41.199 position:50% align:center
