00:20:58.508 --> 00:20:59.759 position:50% align:center
- Kinako?

00:21:00.802 --> 00:21:02.137 position:50% align:center
- Oh.

00:21:02.220 --> 00:21:04.139 position:50% align:center
Hi, Dad.
