00:21:04.681 --> 00:21:05.849 position:50% align:center
A dream?

00:21:06.433 --> 00:21:07.392 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:21:07.475 --> 00:21:09.644 position:50% align:center
[laughing]

00:21:09.728 --> 00:21:12.856 position:50% align:center
This really
is the only thing I can do.

00:21:16.109 --> 00:21:18.737 position:50% align:center
- Ooh, so cold!

00:21:18.820 --> 00:21:20.613 position:50% align:center
Good morning,
Mr. and Mrs. Aoi.

00:21:20.697 --> 00:21:21.823 position:50% align:center
[door creaks closed]
Huh?

00:21:21.906 --> 00:21:23.783 position:50% align:center
I thought Shu
was off baking today.

00:21:23.867 --> 00:21:27.120 position:50% align:center
- Actually, he insisted
on taking Golden Sunrise

00:21:27.203 --> 00:21:29.330 position:50% align:center
