00:21:48.600 --> 00:21:50.101 position:50% align:center
I can do this.

00:21:50.185 --> 00:21:52.771 position:50% align:center
I'll make a real
Golden Sunrise now.

00:21:52.854 --> 00:21:54.731 position:50% align:center
