00:21:54.814 --> 00:21:55.982 position:50% align:center
- [chomps]

00:21:56.733 --> 00:21:59.069 position:50% align:center
Mmm!
So good!

00:21:59.152 --> 00:22:00.779 position:50% align:center
It ain't bad,
part-timer!

00:22:00.862 --> 00:22:03.073 position:50% align:center
- I told you,
