[Junya Enoki, Yuma Uchida,
and Kaito Ishikawa's

00:22:04.616 --> 00:22:05.575 position:50% align:center
"255,255,255"]

00:22:05.658 --> 00:22:08.411 position:50% align:center
Baking bread and being a hero,

00:22:08.495 --> 00:22:10.997 position:50% align:center
