to helping people.

00:22:11.456 --> 00:22:13.708 position:50% align:center
There's no need
to give up on anything.

00:22:14.334 --> 00:22:15.418 position:50% align:center
Isn't that right?

00:22:16.878 --> 00:22:18.588 position:50% align:center
- Hey, Shu!
- Huh?

00:22:19.130 --> 00:22:21.383 position:50% align:center
- Come on!
